headline: A Look At Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) Valuation As New Leadership Team Takes Shape
summary: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) is reshaping its leadership team after announcing the planned retirement of long-serving Chief Operating Officer Chris Isaacson and appointing Scott Johnston and Heidi Fischer to senior executive roles. See our latest analysis for Cboe Global Markets. The executive reshuffle comes as Cboe’s share price trades at US$270.14, with a 30 day share price return of 5.46% and a 90 day share price return of 13.25%, while 1 year and 5 year total shareholder returns of 33.04%...

headline: OSB GROUP PLC - Transaction in Own Shares
summary: OSB GROUP PLC ISIN: GB00BLDRH36027 January 2026 LEI number: 213800ZBKL9BHSL2K459 OSB GROUP PLC (the “Company”) Transaction in Own Shares The Company announces that on 26 January 2026 it had purchased a total of 86,528 of its ordinary shares of £0.01 each (the "ordinary shares") on the London Stock Exchange, CBOE BXE and CBOE CXE, through the Company's broker Citigroup Global Markets Limited as detailed below. The repurchased ordinary shares will be cancelled. London Stock ExchangeCBOE BXECBOE CX
